---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie Policy | Junction Retro">
  <main class="bg-[#F5F5F0] min-h-screen py-24 px-8 md:px-16 selection:bg-indigo-100 selection:text-indigo-900 font-sans">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      
      <a href="/" class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors mb-16 inline-block">
        ← Back to Site
      </a>

      <header class="mb-20 border-b border-slate-200 pb-12">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tighter">
          Cookie Policy
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-indigo-600 font-bold">
          Updated: March 30, 2026
        </p>
      </header>

      <article class="prose prose-slate prose-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        
        <p class="italic text-xl text-slate-800 mb-12">
          To ensure the seamless digital curation of our automotive archive, we utilize cookies to optimize your experience.
        </p>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">1. What are Cookies?</h2>
          <p>
            Cookies are small text files stored on your device that allow us to recognize your preferences and ensure the technical stability of our high-resolution galleries.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">2. Types of Cookies Used</h2>
          <ul class="list-none space-y-6 pl-0">
            <li class="border-l-2 border-slate-200 pl-6">
                <strong class="text-slate-900 block mb-1">Essential Cookies:</strong> 
                Necessary for navigating the archive and accessing secure features. Without these, the site cannot function.
            </li>
            <li class="border-l-2 border-slate-200 pl-6">
                <strong class="text-slate-900 block mb-1">Performance Cookies:</strong> 
                Used anonymously to understand how collectors interact with our vehicle dossiers, allowing us to improve load times for high-resolution PNGs.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">3. Managing Preferences</h2>
          <p>
            You may refuse or delete cookies via your browser settings at any time. Please note that disabling cookies may affect the fluidity of our interactive Svelte components and image carousels.
          </p>
        </section>
      </article>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>